lvm vgcreate myvg across 3 pvs
lv stripe named striped, num stripes 1, stripsize 1MB, total size 20 MB, only use /dev/sd{b,c}
lv mirror named mirror, num mirrors 1, size of 10 extents per mirror, only use /dev/sd{b,c}
create 50% free of /dev/sdd pv named disk, format ext4, extend 100%, mount, only use /dev/sdd